  "_special_DC_comment": "10 CuSn runs (18358-18368) flagged in Runs.hpp as special drift-chamber configuration. They fall inside the INBENDING CuSn span, not the outbending production. Recorded, not applied: the original applied them to nothing either, and inventing a cut here would be inventing physics. If they are ever to be excluded, that belongs in a farm config's exclude_runs with a stated reason.",
